isConceptClean

public boolean isConceptClean(int concept_id)
                       throws DataSourceException
Given a concept_id this method returns true, if the concept is clean, i.e. if all entries in the CRACS tables which are part of this concept have status in "R" or "U".

Parameters:
concept_id - int
Returns:
true if the concept is clean, otherwise false.
Throws:
DataSourceException - if failed to check the concept id.
